#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:9
msgid "Sphinx + ablog でDraftを自動公開するための自動ビルドの設定"
msgstr ""
"Setting up automatic build to automatically publish Draft with Sphinx + "
"ablog"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:11
msgid ""
"Sphinx + ablog "
"でのブログ運営では「投稿日を未来日にしておく」ことで、ドラフト記事を準備できます。しかし、公開日以降にビルドが走らない限りWebサイトには反映されません。本記事では自動ビルドを実行する方法を考察します。"
msgstr ""
"When running a blog with Sphinx + ablog, you can prepare draft articles by "
"setting the post date to a future date. However, it will not be reflected on"
" the website unless the build is run after the release date. This article "
"looks at how to run automated builds."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:19
msgid "背景と課題"
msgstr "Background and issues"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:21
msgid ""
"ablog では ``.. post:: YYYY-MM-DD`` "
"のように記事日付を設定しますが、日付が未来である場合、その記事はドラフトとして無視されます。"
msgstr ""
"ablog sets the article date as ``.. post:: YYYY-MM-DD``, but if the date is "
"in the future, the article will be ignored as a draft."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:23
msgid "例えば2025-05-05現在、以下のような記事を書いたとしても："
msgstr ""
"For example, as of 2025-05-05, even if you write an article like the "
"following:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:33
msgid "この記事が実際にビルド出力されるのは、 **6月1日以降に Sphinx を再ビルドしたとき** です。"
msgstr ""
"This article will actually be output when Sphinx is rebuilt after June 1st."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:35
msgid ""
"本サイトは、Netlifyでサイトを公開していますが、Netlifyでは GitHub への push "
"がビルドトリガとなっているため、「未来記事の自動公開」には対応していません。"
msgstr ""
"This site is published on Netlify, but because Netlify uses a push to GitHub"
" as a build trigger, it does not support \"automatic publication of future "
"articles.\""

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:37
msgid "そのため、 **未来日を迎えた後に自動で再ビルドを実行する仕組み** については別途検討する必要があります。"
msgstr ""
"Therefore, it is necessary to separately consider **a mechanism to "
"automatically rebuild after a future date**."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:40
msgid "本サイトの環境"
msgstr "Environment of this site"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:41
msgid "本サイトは、以下のような環境で運用しています。同じような環境の方は参考にしてください。"
msgstr ""
"This site is operated in the following environment. Please refer to this if "
"you are in a similar environment."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:43
msgid "**Sphinx** + **ablog** で構築"
msgstr "Built with **Sphinx** + **ablog**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:44
msgid "**GitHub** でソースコード管理"
msgstr "Source code management with **GitHub**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:45
msgid "**Netlify** でホスティング"
msgstr "Hosted with **Netlify**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:48
msgid "解決策：GitHub Actions × Netlify Build Hook"
msgstr "Solution: GitHub Actions × Netlify Build Hook"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:50
msgid ""
"Netlify では、特定の URL に対して POST リクエストを送信することで、任意のタイミングでビルドを実行できる **Build Hook**"
" 機能を提供しています。"
msgstr ""
"Netlify provides a **Build Hook** feature that allows you to run a build at "
"any time by sending a POST request to a specific URL."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:52
msgid ""
"この Build Hook に対して、GitHub Actions "
"の定期実行（cron）機能を使って毎日決まった時間にアクセスすれば、自動的にビルドが発生します。"
msgstr ""
"If you access this Build Hook at a fixed time every day using the periodic "
"execution (cron) function of GitHub Actions, a build will occur "
"automatically."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:54
msgid "これにより、未来日を過ぎた ablog の記事が毎日チェックされ、自動公開されるようになります。"
msgstr ""
"With this, ablog articles past the future date will be checked every day and"
" automatically published."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:57
msgid "設定手順"
msgstr "Setting procedure"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:59
msgid "**NetlifyでBuild Hookを作成**"
msgstr "**Create a Build Hook with Netlify**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:61
msgid "Netlify の管理画面にアクセス"
msgstr "Access the Netlify admin screen"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:62
msgid "対象サイト →「Site configrations」→「Build & deploy」→「Build hooks」"
msgstr "Target site → “Site configrations” → “Build & deploy” → “Build hooks”"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:63
msgid ""
"Add build hook - Hook name: 任意（例: `Daily Scheduled Deploy`） - Branch: `main`"
" （または使用中のブランチ）"
msgstr ""
"Add build hook - Hook name: Any (e.g. `Daily Scheduled Deploy`) - Branch: "
"`main` (or branch in use)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:67
msgid ""
"作成後に表示される URL（例：`https://api.netlify.com/build_hooks/xxxxxxxxxxxxxx`）を控えておく"
msgstr ""
"Make a note of the URL that will be displayed after creation (e.g. "
"`https://api.netlify.com/build_hooks/xxxxxxxxxxxxxx`)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:69
msgid "**GitHub Secrets に Build Hook を登録（セキュリティ対応）**"
msgstr "**Register Build Hook in GitHub Secrets (security compatible)**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:71
msgid ""
"Build Hook の URL は知られてしまうと誰でもビルドを発動できてしまうため、**GitHub Secrets** で安全に管理します。"
msgstr ""
"If the Build Hook URL is known, anyone can trigger the build, so we safely "
"manage it with **GitHub Secrets**."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:73
msgid "GitHub リポジトリ → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions"
msgstr "GitHub repository → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:74
msgid ""
"「New repository secret」 - Name: `NETLIFY_BUILD_HOOK` - Value: Netlify で取得した "
"Build Hook URL"
msgstr ""
"\"New repository secret\" - Name: `NETLIFY_BUILD_HOOK` - Value: Build Hook "
"URL obtained with Netlify"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:78
msgid "**GitHub Actions ワークフローを作成**"
msgstr "**Create a GitHub Actions workflow**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:80
msgid "リポジトリの `.github/workflows/` フォルダに以下のようなファイルを作成："
msgstr ""
"Create a file like the following in the `.github/workflows/` folder of your "
"repository:"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:83
msgid ".github/workflows/netlify-scheduled-deploy.yml"
msgstr ".github/workflows/netlify-scheduled-deploy.yml"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:102
msgid "🔹 `workflow_dispatch` を追加することで、必要に応じて GitHub 上から手動でビルドを実行することもできます。"
msgstr ""
"🔹 You can also run builds manually from GitHub if needed by adding "
"`workflow_dispatch`."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:104
msgid "**コミットして GitHub に反映**"
msgstr "**Commit and reflect on GitHub**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:106
msgid "作成した `.yml` をコミット・プッシュすれば、毎日自動的に Netlify ビルドが行われるようになります。"
msgstr ""
"If you commit and push the `.yml` you created, Netlify build will be "
"performed automatically every day."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:109
msgid "セキュリティ上の注意点"
msgstr "Security considerations"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:111
msgid "**Build Hook URL はトークンと同じ扱いで、絶対に公開しないこと**"
msgstr ""
"**Build Hook URL is treated like a token and should never be made public**"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:112
msgid "`.env` ファイルで管理する場合は、`.gitignore` に含めてリポジトリに含めないようにする"
msgstr ""
"If you manage it with a `.env` file, include it in `.gitignore` so that it "
"is not included in the repository."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:113
msgid "GitHub Secrets を使えば、ログ出力などにもマスクが自動でかかるため安心"
msgstr ""
"If you use GitHub Secrets, you can rest assured that log output etc. will be"
" automatically masked."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:116
msgid "補足"
msgstr "supplement"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:118
msgid "cron は UTC ベースのため、日本時間（JST）で定期実行したい場合は9時間引く必要があります"
msgstr ""
"cron is based on UTC, so if you want to run it regularly in Japan Time "
"(JST), you need to subtract 9 hours."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:119
msgid "毎日 0 時 JST に実行したい場合 → `cron: '0 15 * * *'`"
msgstr "If you want to run it every day at 0:00 JST → `cron: '0 15 * * *'`"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:120
msgid "週次・月次への変更も可能（例: 毎週月曜 JST 0 時 → `'0 15 * * 1'`）"
msgstr ""
"It is also possible to change to weekly/monthly (e.g. every Monday at 0:00 "
"JST → `'0 15 * * 1'`)"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:123
msgid "まとめ"
msgstr "summary"

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:125
msgid ""
"ablog で未来日記事を予約投稿として管理した場合、Netlifyでホスティングしている以上は、通常はgit "
"pushしない限りビルドされないため、公開されません。 今回、Netlify の Build Hook と GitHub Actions の "
"`cron` 実行を組み合わせることで、 **定期的にビルドをトリガし、記事の自動公開を実現** しました。"
msgstr ""
"If you manage a future article as a scheduled post on ablog, it will not be "
"published unless it is hosted on Netlify because it will not be built unless"
" you git push it. This time, by combining Netlify's Build Hook and GitHub "
"Actions' `cron` execution, we were able to **trigger builds periodically and"
" automatically publish articles**."

#: ../../../blog/posts/2025-05-05-scheduled-ablog-build.rst:128
msgid "本スタックは、GitHub Actions + Netlify の組み合わせで、コストもかからないのがうれしいところです。"
msgstr ""
"This stack is a combination of GitHub Actions + Netlify, and the good thing "
"about it is that it doesn't cost anything."

